 difference is that you ought to select the 'OpenTriangle_AGA' picture
 (yes indeed 8) ) and that you have to add the following line to the
 tooltypes of the @{"Magic Copper" LINK "What is Magic Copper?"} icon:

  EFFECT 0x5D625D 0xCBAE91 0 OpenTriangle_AGA

@ENDNODE



