@NODE "Gotcha!"

 Gotcha!
 -------

 No way! No pictures. It would make the archive too big. It's the brain
 you know, not the head 8). I wanted to include a picture of my brain but
 since it's so incredibly complex... After my calculations, I came unto a
 result of 2,457,925,129,099 bytes for an lha archive.
 I cannot guarantee that this number is correct. It was calculated with
 my pocket calculator, running on an INTEL processor. So...

@ENDNODE



